{"tid":1142340,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」藝人林子善，沽東環細戶，4年微賺141 萬。","createTime":"2019-05-07T04:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T13:50:06.000Z","uid":228794,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"775a065515c9e8d725542ce92a730dfdb71e82a2","tid":1142340,"uid":228794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"樓價回升加上交投暢旺，吸引不少名人沽貨，其中藝人林子善近日亦售出持有的東涌東環II（東環第2期）細戶，帳面獲利141.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，東環II 2A座高層7室，實用面積384平方呎1房，上月以610萬放盤，因單位樓層夠高，獲上車客睇中，近日最終議價至600萬元成交，呎價15,625元。<br />\n<br />\nEPRC（經濟地產庫）顯示，單位登記業主為藝人林子善，早於2015年9月以458.4萬一手價入市，持貨3年8個月左右，帳面升價141.6萬或30.9%。資料顯示，是次成交單位的同座同室戶，今年曾錄3宗買賣成交，造價517萬至565萬，今次「6球」造價較高6.2%至16.1%。"},{"pid":"8b06c582ba75e17fcd49759d78773bf2be6b8bf4","tid":1142340,"uid":88104,"like":212,"dislike":1,"score":211,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"佢收人情都有賺啦"},{"pid":"2e33b95950e7bc48aa64de0cfe358c25ec4b995f","tid":1142340,"uid":107364,"like":113,"dislike":12,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:18:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1e4930fe724c4de6cb65d511687436bbd660ab9","tid":1142340,"uid":83328,"like":18,"dislike":38,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"4年先賺百萬其實好濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b522acd71ebd4c1f48a9a5a6e8f37e526f90a6d","tid":1142340,"uid":38930,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"44個月 140萬除開每個月都袋3萬"},{"pid":"e9a22e42ea64158a34e860acec06325734f45cc9","tid":1142340,"uid":18012,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"quote":{"pid":"d1e4930fe724c4de6cb65d511687436bbd660ab9","tid":1142340,"uid":83328,"like":18,"dislike":38,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"4年先賺百萬其實好濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:21:32.000Z","msg":"1個月都接近30k<br />\n連登果然個個搵50k<br />\n<br />\n30k 都濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal